Package: autotargets
Title: Automatic targets Pipeline Generation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Beau", "", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "beau@example.com")
Description: Automatically generates targets pipelines by scanning R files for
    functions and constants, mapping them to tar_target() definitions based on
    function arguments. No AST analysis or manual DAG specification required.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
